column5: Oh man, I feel so bad.  I just realized that the little thing that says messenger (0), was wrong on my screen.  When i went into my inbox, i had 48 unread messages.  People giving and asking for advice.  For all those who sent me messages and didn't receive one back, i am truly sorry.  Feel like such an ass!  lovetofish
No worries at all. It's too bad you didn't get to answer that little skill testing question for the new, fully equipped bass boat though. Maybe next time.
he also missed out on the free fishing trip every month in Florida airfare and spending money included for life too....   Art
It happens lovetofish. fergetaboutit.  Roy I seen that,but thought it was spam,so deleted it.LOL
He also missed a week long party with Charlie Sheen, porn stars and hookers included.
